        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="external-resources">
        <h2>Further Reading</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://www.nightingale.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Nightingale-Conant — Earl Nightingale's Archive</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://psycnet.apa.org/record/1992-98075-000" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Gollwitzer — Implementation Intentions Research</a></li>
