        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="book-recommendations">
        <h2>Recommended Books</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>The Strangest Secret</strong> — Earl Nightingale (audio and transcript)</li>
          <li><strong>Lead the Field</strong> — Earl Nightingale</li>
          <li><strong>Think and Grow Rich</strong> — Napoleon Hill</li>
          <li><strong>Psycho-Cybernetics</strong> — Maxwell Maltz</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

